item.title: LimeZ - Aftermath [Dubstep/Chill]
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Nice chords! Lake feels a little strong. Personally, I like the hats! It’s nice and almost creepy. Drop is a little weird. Drums should have been more varied imo. Also, not sure if the chords for the bass in the drop fit that well

Versatility: 7/10
Creativity: 8/10
Predictability: 9/10
Use of Instruments/Automation: 5/10
Feeling: 7/10

Overall: 36/50 Not bad at all my dude

item.title: LimeZ - Aftermath [Dubstep/Chill]
item.dc:creator: DJ_La_Rocca
item.description:
Nice bells. And baseline. Didn’t like the sudden change when the hi hats came along. You need to work on transitions a bit more. U had sudden chnages without expectancy. Otherwise nice drop. Maybe the chords could of followed along better and at a lower octave.

Keep it up
